Class DiscardPowerUpCard

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.limperio.nicotera.italia.events.events_by_client.ClientEvent
      • it.polimi.se2019.limperio.nicotera.italia.events.events_by_client.DiscardPowerUpCard
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class DiscardPowerUpCard
extends ClientEvent
    Event generated when the player decide to discard a power up card to pay an effect, a weapon, the reload of a weapon or when he wants to use targeting or tagback.
    Author:
    Pietro L'Imperio.
